'''六氟合锗酸'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为H<sub>2</sub>[GeF<sub>6</sub>]，它可由[[锗|锗]]和[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]、[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]反应<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Metal Finishing Society of Japan|volume=20|issue=8|language=ja|issn=1884-3395|date=1969|pages=396–399|doi=10.4139/sfj1950.20.396|url=http://joi.jlc.jst.go.jp/JST.Journalarchive/sfj1950/20.396?from=CrossRef|title=Acid Chemical Etching for Ge-In Alloyed Junction Element|accessdate=2021-01-26|author=Jyun-ichiro Kawada}}</ref>，或[[二氧化锗|二氧化锗]]溶于[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]得到，可存在于氢氟酸溶液中。<ref>Tananaev, I. V.; Nikolaev, N. S.; Buslaev, Yu. A. Phase equilibrium in the systems HF-​MF<sub>4</sub>-​H<sub>2</sub>O. ''Fiz.-Khim. Analiz, Akad. Nauk SSSR, Sibirsk. Otd., Inst. Neorgan. Khim. Tr. Yubileinoi Konf., Novosibirsk'', 1963 (1960): 85-92. CAN62: 19221.</ref>它可以在碱性条件下水解：<ref>Ryss, I. G.; Kulish, N. F. Kinetics of the hydrolysis of hexafluorogermanate ion, GeF<sub>6</sub><sup>-​-</sup>. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1963 (8): 342-348. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>
: GeF<sub>6</sub><sup>2−</sup> + 4 OH<sup>−</sup> → GeO<sub>2</sub> + 6 F<sup>−</sup> + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O
它和水合[[肼|肼]]加热反应，可以沉淀出(N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>Ge<sub>7</sub>O<sub>15</sub>(OH)·2.5H<sub>2</sub>O。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Microporous and Mesoporous Materials|volume=131|issue=1-3|language=en|date=2010-06|pages=282–288|doi=10.1016/j.micromeso.2010.01.003|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1387181110000041|title=Synthesis, structure and properties of hydrazinium germanate pharmacosiderite, (N2H5)3Ge7O15(OH)·2.5H2O|accessdate=2021-01-26|author=Sergey N. Britvin, Dar’ya V. Spiridonova, Oleg I. Siidra, Andriy Lotnyk, Lorenz Kienle, Sergey V. Krivovichev, Wulf Depmeier}}</ref>它和[[氟化锂|氟化锂]]反应，可以得到六氟合锗酸锂。<ref>石世昆. 六氟锗酸锂的合成方法及其新用途. CN 201310127585.</ref>

